-- Sanofi May Raise Genzyme Bid, Looking for Financing, WSJ Says
-- B y   S y l v i a   W i e r
-- 2010-09-26T20:44:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/sanofi-seeks-financing-for-higher-genzyme-bid-wall-street-journal-reports.html
Sanofi-Aventis SA is considering
raising its bid for Genzyme Corp. and is arranging more
financing, the Wall Street Journal reported, citing unidentified
people familiar with the matter.  Citigroup Inc. and Bank of America Corp. were approached by
Sanofi, the Journal said, citing the people.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
